<br>
My group was on the second floor of the Tower of Frozen Shadow trying to anger the Librarian so that we could get a key to the third.  Towards the end of the evening, we'd had two angry librarians spawn, and had killed three regular librarians and their assistants.  The only spell drop was Tumultuous Strength.  Just as we're about to port out, someone higher up in the tower /ooc's Ro's Fiery Sundering.  After communicating with them in /tells for a few moments, they tell me that they've got several in their guild bank, and that four more just dropped that night.  I offer to buy it, and they offer to just give it to me.<br>
<br>
Met up with them in the Gnoll Camp.  I guess the drop rate really HAS been increased.  Glad I got mine before they nerf it.  ;)<br>
